difficulty: A task was easy if the table was small and well organized with everything labeled. It was difficult when there was a lot of information, too much spacing, not enough spacing, the table didn’t fit the phone screen, or if the information wasn’t labeled.
format: Tables with large blocks of badly formatted text were made me unsatisfied. A satisfying table was small with good spacing and minimal information.
comments: The only annoying issue was the table not fitting on the screen in any orientation.
